race.description: Carpet Call Qtis Three-Year-Old Maiden Plate
race.comment: READY FOR AIMEE (14) is back from a 143-day spell. Has only raced once, leading for home over this distance at Doomben only to be swamped close to home. Trialling in good style and this looks a nice race to launch the second campaign. CROKER (2) is a gelding by Spirit Of Boom on debut. Has won a trial at this track. Trained here and the inside draw is an aid for a first starter so could go close. HIDDEN FUTURE (12) is a filly by Impending making her first appearance. Was runner-up in a trial at Beaudesert. Draws well so can play a role. MISHANI PRINCE (5) should be approaching peak fitness and could be close to a win after placing in his last two runs in the city.
